@harness   mk, reaper.TrackFX_GetCount, reaper.TrackFX_Delete, r._state.projectTracks, r._state.trackGuids

# Intent
  (none)

# Helpers
  @fn mkWm(harness)  @ 4-10
  @fn seedSource(h, guid)  @ 12-17
  @fn source(guid)  @ 19-22
  @fn mintFx(wm, ident, opts)  @ 26-31
      -- Mint an fx on scratch (as wm:addFxNode does in production) so the node enters the
      -- graph carrying a live guid; reconcile then MOVES it onto its track.
  @fn audioEdge(from, to)  @ 33-35
  @fn audioOnlyJSFX()  @ 39
      -- Scan the test JSFX as audio-only. A MIDI-capable scan brackets the chain with a bus-route
