  @case 'enableLive: idempotent — second call does not double-subscribe'  [harness]  @ 96-115
  @case 'wm:load re-reads REAPER; a behind-the-back FX delete drops from the graph'  [harness]  @ 118-140
  @case 'enableLive: a settled project reconciles to zero ops and opens no undo block'  [harness]  @ 143-170

